title: SAP University Alliances North America  Faculty Winter Workshops 2017
content:
Professors from SAP University Alliances member institutions from across the Americas are invited to attend the SAP University Alliances Winter Workshop.

Workshops are held at Sam Houston State University in January. Each workshop session features several topics.  Topics run in parallel, each participant may only register for one topic each week.  Registration begins October 15, 2016.  Please register early to secure a seat in the workshop of your choice. If you are unable to attend, please contact us at uap.na@sap.com to cancel your reservation. To ensure a positive workshop experience, seats are limited in each topic and registration will close when capacity is reached

title: EMEA UCC Portal
content: The SAP UA EMEA Portal provides all important pieces of information and services for the users of the SAP UCC Magdeburg, SAP UCC Munich, as well as ACC in Sierre, St. Petersburg, and Vienna.
